name: agswap Token
description: The world's first decentralized trading platform for transaction deflation mining, AGSwap, realizes multi-chain sharing of digital assets by constructing a multi-chain ecological deployment system. AGSwap provides multiple public chains and cross-chain aggregate transaction functions, which integrates cross-chain liquidity , To realize the intelligent scene of multiple public chains, and to create a seamless exchange and interoperability application of multi-chain native assets.
